  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573260/extras/060b9fa0fb3f04ea1da011f52c4713e7.poster.avif?t=1745329588\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573260/extras/060b9fa0fb3f04ea1da011f52c4713e7.webm?t=1745329588\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3573260/extras/060b9fa0fb3f04ea1da011f52c4713e7.mp4?t=1745329588\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>110+ Unique Heroes</strong>: Choose from a diverse set of heroes and create powerful synergies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Deck Building</strong>: Recruit new heroes after each battle and craft the best team.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Auto-Battle System</strong>: Watch your heroes fight while you refine your strategy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Roguelike Elements</strong>: Every run offers new choices, making each playthrough unique.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A perfect blend of <strong>strategy and luck</strong> in a roguelike auto-battler!<br>Build your deck and take on the challenge!</p>",
